title: Git Mini Session
summary: This 2-hour Git mini course is designed to give you a comprehensive understanding of the version control system.
You will learn how to create Git repositories, track changes, work collaboratively with others, and resolve conflicts.
By the end of the course, you will have the skills to confidently and effectively manage your projects using Git.

title: Figma Mini Session
summary: You will learn the basics of using the popular design tool Figma in this 2-hour mini course.
From creating artboards to designing interfaces, you will gain practical skills that can be applied to your own projects
By the end of the course, you will have a solid foundation in using Figma for your design work.

title: MySQL Mini Session
summary: This 2-hour MySQL mini course provides an introduction to the fundamentals of database management using MySQL.
Participants will learn how to create and manipulate databases, tables, and queries using MySQL
The course also covers basic data manipulation techniques such as filtering, sorting, and joining data.
By the end of the course, students will have a foundational understanding of how to effectively use MySQL to manage and analyze data.
